videos.headline: Jackson connects with Smith for 31-yard strike
videos.description: Louisville QB Lamar Jackson gets his team in the red zone after throwing a 31-yard pass to Jaylen Smith, who makes sure to lay a hard hit on a Florida State defender before stepping out of bounds.

videos.headline: Lamar Jackson run for 2 yds for a TD
videos.description: Lamar Jackson run for 2 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Jackson off to another hot start with second rushing TD
videos.description: Louisville QB Lamar Jackson navigates around the Florida State defense running 14 yards in to the end zone for his second rushing touchdown of the game.

videos.headline: Lamar Jackson run for 33 yds for a 1ST down
videos.description: Lamar Jackson run for 33 yds to the FlaSt 27 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Evan O'Hara 48 yd FG missed off the upright
videos.description: Evan O'Hara 48 yd FG MISSED

videos.headline: Francois cuts into deficit with 20-yard TD pass
videos.description: Florida State QB Deondre Francois throws a 20-yard touchdown pass to Auden Tate to cut their deficit against Louisville.

videos.headline: Louisville RB Smith barrels his way into end zone
videos.description: Louisville RB Jeremy Smith runs straight through the Florida State defense for the 2-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Bad handoff exchange results in Louisville ball
videos.description: Florida State QB Deondre Francois does not hand the ball off to Dalvin Cook cleanly, leading to a fumble and Louisville recovering the loose ball.

videos.headline: Jackson continues to roll, finds Smith for TD
videos.description: Louisville QB Lamar Jackson throws over the middle to Jaylen Smith for a 4-yard touchdown pass, giving the Cardinals a 28-10 lead over Florida State.

videos.headline: Deondre Francois sacked by Devonte Fields to force punt before Halftime
videos.description: Deondre Francois sacked by Devonte Fields for a loss of 12 yards to the FlaSt 29

videos.headline: Lee Corso can't believe this catch
videos.description: Louisville WR James Quick makes a great catch between his legs for a 45-yard gain, to the amazement of Lee Corso.

videos.headline: Lamar Jackson scores third rushing TD of first half
videos.description: Louisville QB Lamar Jackson is having no problem solving Florida State's defense, this time running one yard for his third rushing touchdown of the first half.

videos.headline: Louisville pads lead with 69-yard punt return TD
videos.description: Louisville punt returner Logan Tyler races through the Florida State defense and takes the punt 69 yards in for the touchdown, widening Louisville's lead over Florida State.

videos.headline: Lamar Jackson owned Florida State in the first half
videos.description: Louisville QB Lamar Jackson had no problems carving up Florida State's defense in the first half running for three touchdown and throwing for one.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Lamar Jackson owned Florida State in the first half) 2016/09/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Louisville RB Smith finds end zone for a second time
videos.description: Louisville RB Jeremy Smith runs for a 1-yard touchdown, putting the Cardinals ahead of the Seminoles 49-10.

videos.headline: Louisville sack for huge loss forces 4th down
videos.description: Deondre Francois sacked by Josh Harvey-Clemons for a loss of 11 yards to the FlaSt 29

videos.headline: Jackson runs through FSU defense for touchdown
videos.description: Louisville quarterback Lamar Jackson blows past the entire Florida State defense for a 47-yard touchdown, his fourth rushing score of the game.

videos.headline: Deondre Francois throws interception
videos.description: Deondre Francois pass intercepted Chucky Williams return for 36 yds to the FlaSt 10

videos.headline: Louisville RB Radcliff bulldozes his way into end zone
videos.description: Louisville RB Brandon Radcliff runs straight into the Florida State defense, but is determined not to be brought down and makes his way in to the end zone for a 6-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Tate makes spectacular late TD grab
videos.description: Florida State WR Auden Tate skies and comes down with a great, 12-yard touchdown catch late in their game against Louisville.

videos.headline: Louisville more than just Lamar Jackson
videos.description: Check out just how on point Louisville's defense was against No. 2 Florida State in Week 3.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Louisville more than just Lamar Jackson) 2016/09/17 ESHEET
